        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "\u0007  If you are in SPLITV mode,"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "- If the second task occupies less than ten columns of the screen,"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "SPF/PC swaps the position and columns counts of the sessions."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "- If the second task occupies more than ten columns of the screen,"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "SPF/PC activates the second task and moves the cursor to it,"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "without changing the split point."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "\u0007  If you are in MVSPLIT mode, the split is at the midpoint,SPF/PC"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "activates the second task and moves the cursor to it, without"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "changing the split point."
